high_descs: Turn left then turn right and go forward and turn left to face the countertop.
Pick up the banana from the counter.
Turn about and move forward to reach near the sink.
Wash the banana in the sink and take it out.
Keep the banana on the flat area of the sink.

high_descs: Head rotate and walk near the countertop.
Pick the banana near the microwave table.
Turn back and place the banana inside the sink.

Place the banana on the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the counter top.
Pick up banana from the desk.
Turn around towards the sink at the back.
Place banana left side on the sink.
anns.task_desc: washing banana on the sink and placing it clean.
